abstract: United States will host qualifying soccer match for 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics.
lead_paragraph: North American, Central American and Caribbean teams will compete in a qualifying tournament in October for two spots at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics.

headline.main: U.S. to Host Qualifying Event for 2016 Olympics
